{"title":"Procurement at VOSA","public_updated_at":"2014-08-09T11:44:41Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n<p>The Vehicle and Operator Services Agency (VOSA) closed on 31 March 2014. It has been replaced by the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/driver-and-vehicle-standards-agency/about/procurement\">Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency</a> (DVSA). This is the information about VOSA that was published at the point that it closed. It is no longer current.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-we-do\">What we do</h2>\n\n<p>Our procurement unit makes sure that we:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>follow European procurement directives</li>\n  <li>get best value for money in everything we buy</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We do this by identifying the most cost-effective methods of buying and contracting for a wide range of goods and services.</p>\n\n<p>We do this in 2 stages:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>advertising, tendering and award of contracts</li>\n  <li>contract management to monitor the performance of suppliers and the quality of goods and services supplied</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"guidance-for-our-suppliers\">Guidance for our suppliers</h2>\n\n<p>You can read a guide to <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tendering-for-public-sector-contracts\">tendering for public sector contracts</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The following documents contain our conditions of contract:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/general-conditions-of-contract-for-services\">general conditions of contract for services</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/general-conditions-of-contract-for-goods\">general conditions of contract for goods</a></li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/purchase-order-conditions-of-contract\">purchase order conditions of contract</a> (typically for goods and services valued at less than Â£25,000)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-contact-us\">How to contact us</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact postal-address\" id=\"contact_1128\">\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <h3>DVSA procurement</h3>\n\n    <div class=\"vcard contact-inner\">\n        <p class=\"adr\">\n<span class=\"fn\">Procurement Unit </span><br>\n<span class=\"street-address\">DVSA\n<br>\nBerkeley House \n<br>\nCroydon Street</span><br>\n<span class=\"region\">Bristol</span><br>\n<span class=\"postal-code\">BS5 0DA </span>\n</p>\n\n\n        <div class=\"email-url-number\">\n            <p class=\"email\">\n              <span class=\"type\">Email</span>\n              <a class=\"email\" href=\"mailto:procurement@vosa.gsi.gov.uk\">procurement@vosa.gsi.gov.uk</a>\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tel\">\n              <span class=\"type\">Fax</span>\n              0117 954 3413\n            </p>\n        </div>\n\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>","organisation":"f3dc9b48-1119-4130-9bc4-98f5e3fd7fab","tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/organisations/vehicle-and-operator-services-agency/about/procurement","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"procurement","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","first_published_at":"2016-05-13T16:11:36Z","base_path":"/government/organisations/vehicle-and-operator-services-agency/about/procurement","description":"How we buy goods and services, and how you can work with us. \r\n","content_id":"5f55d72b-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA79","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/vehicle-and-operator-services-agency","base_path":"/government/organisations/vehicle-and-operator-services-agency","content_id":"f3dc9b48-1119-4130-9bc4-98f5e3fd7fab","description":null,"document_type":"organisation","locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-10-15T14:35:30Z","schema_name":"placeholder